show.description: In a world of greed, betrayal, and hidden identities, Natasha Nanda battles her stepsister Trisha and her manipulative father while secretly yearning for love from her bodyguard, Jai. Trapped in a web of lies, jealousy, and power struggles, Natasha is torn between sacrifice and survival. As truths unravel, dangerous rivalries push the family toward shocking consequences where love, revenge, and redemption collide. Watch now.
